    <div class="info-section">
      <div class="info-title">Mapping (A-Z → Angka):</div>
      <div id="mappingInfo">
        A→4, B→8, C→01, D→02, E→3, F→03, G→6, H→04, I→1, L→1, O→0, S→5, T→7, Z→2<br>
        Huruf lain memakai angka unik 2 digit.
      </div>
      <div class="info-title" style="margin-top: 12px;">Contoh:</div>
      <div>
        hello → h3110<br>
        selamat → 53140747<br>
